TODOApplication-Frequently Asked Questions(FAQ)

This "Frequently Asked Questions" document will be updated continually to accomodate new information with respect to new updates and changes on the app and will be used in the app to help users find answers to their questions.

What is TODOApplication?

TODOApplication is an open-source ToDo and reminder application which provides a user with simplicity as well as productivity. It comes with a clean materialistic design. 
It was built by Pronoy Mukherjee

How do I create a To-do?

Upon opening the app, this can done by pressing the '+' option at the bottom right of the screen

How do I create and add a category?

This is done by pressing the '+' button at the top most right of the screen and adding your desired category.

Can i create reminders?

Yes you can create reminders upon addition of your todo.

Is TODOApplication safe to install on my phone?

Yes, it very safe

Is TODOApplication available on other platforms apart from android?

No, its only available for android system

Where can I leave feedbacks or suggestions or report bugs?

You can report them directly on:
Our Github issue page - https://github.com/Pronoy999/TODOApplication
